  "detailed_description": "Silent Shores is a first-person open world horror game where you play as a father searching for his missing son on an abandoned island. Explore eerie abandoned buildings, drive through mysterious forests, and uncover the dark secrets of the island. But beware, you are not alone.<br><br><br><strong>Explore Silent Shores by car or on foot.</strong><br>You have the freedom to explore Silent Shores how you please on foot or by car<br>The choice is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/8de239e34927bec027255da883f43db4.poster.avif?t=1732078854\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/8de239e34927bec027255da883f43db4.webm?t=1732078854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/8de239e34927bec027255da883f43db4.mp4?t=1732078854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Explore Abandoned Buildings </strong><br>Explore abandoned buildings and find clues that will lead you to your son.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/2a02c065d6377434e7ade37fe147537d.poster.avif?t=1732078854\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/2a02c065d6377434e7ade37fe147537d.webm?t=1732078854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443050/extras/2a02c065d6377434e7ade37fe147537d.mp4?t=1732078854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>You are not alone.</strong><br>Whether outside, or indoors, Evil may be lurking around the corner.<br><br><spa